'''陳家諾'''（{{lang-en|Arnold Chan}}，{{bd|1967年|6月10日|2017年|9月14日|catIdx=Chan}}），[[加拿大|加拿大]]華裔政治人物和律師，[[加拿大自由黨|加拿大自由黨]]黨員，2014年-17年間擔任[[加拿大國會下議院|加拿大國會下議院]]議員，代表[[安大略省|安大略省]][[多倫多|多倫多]]的[[士嘉堡－愛靜閣選區|士嘉堡－愛靜閣選區]]。

==生平==
1967年於加拿大出生，父母於1966年移居自[[香港|香港]]<ref name="星島140701">{{cite news |url=http://news.singtao.ca/toronto/2014-07-01/headline1404202060d5120503.html |title=港父親為兒移民 陳家諾不負重望 |publisher=《[[星島日報|星島日報]]》加東版 |date=2014-07-01 |accessdate=2017-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140824192305/http://news.singtao.ca/toronto/2014-07-01/headline1404202060d5120503.html |archive-date=2014-08-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。他於[[安大略省|安大略省]][[士嘉堡|士嘉堡]]市（後來併入[[多倫多|多倫多]]市）長大，從當地的[[诺尔曼·白求恩中学|诺尔曼·白求恩中学]]畢業後到[[多倫多大學|多倫多大學]]就讀，先後獲取政治學學士和碩士學位<ref name="CNW140430">{{cite web | url=http://www.newswire.ca/news-releases/arnold-chan-green-lit-as-candidate-for-scarborough-agincourt-federal-liberal-nomination-514186001.html | publisher=Canada Newswire | title=Arnold Chan Green Lit As Candidate for Scarborough-Agincourt Federal Liberal Nomination | date=2014-04-30 | accessdate=2017-09-15 | archive-date=2017-09-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170915113418/http://www.newswire.ca/news-releases/arnold-chan-green-lit-as-candidate-for-scarborough-agincourt-federal-liberal-nomination-514186001.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="about">{{cite web | url=http://achan.liberal.ca/biography/ | publisher=[[加拿大自由黨|加拿大自由黨]] | title=Biography | accessdate=2017-09-15 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170915024244/http://achan.liberal.ca/biography/ | archivedate=2017-09-15 }}</ref>。他其後到[[卑詩大學|卑詩大學]]修讀法律，1993年取得法學士學位<ref>{{cite web | url=http://historyproject.allard.ubc.ca/law-history-project/profile/arnold-g-chan | publisher=[[卑詩大學|卑詩大學]]法學院 | title=Arnold G Chan | accessdate=2017-09-15 | archive-date=2017-09-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170916053006/https://historyproject.allard.ubc.ca/law-history-project/profile/arnold-g-chan | dead-url=no }}</ref>後供職多倫多數家律師事務所，專注發展和規劃法<ref name="Citizen140915">{{cite news |url=http://ottawacitizen.com/news/national/q-and-a-liberal-mp-arnold-chan-on-moving-from-the-backroom-into-the-spotlight |title=Q&A: Liberal MP Arnold Chan on moving from the backroom into the spotlight |publisher=《渥太華公民報》 |first=Jason |last=Fekete |date=2014-09-15 |accessdate=2017-09-15 |archive-date=2017-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170915204521/http://ottawacitizen.com/news/national/q-and-a-liberal-mp-arnold-chan-on-moving-from-the-backroom-into-the-spotlight |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他其後重返多大進修並獲取城市規劃碩士學位<ref name="CNW140430"/><ref name="about"/>。

==政治生涯==
陳家諾自16歲已經加入[[加拿大自由黨|聯邦自由黨]]，成年後涉足安大略省級政治，曾參與[[安大略自由黨|安大略自由黨]]候選人菲臘斯（{{lang|en|Gerry Phillips}}）角逐[[安大略省議會|省議會]]士嘉堡－愛靜閣選區議席的競選工作<ref name="星島140701"/>，並從2000年-03年出任在野安大略自由黨黨魁[[道爾頓·麥堅迪|麥堅迪]]的行政助理。該黨於2003年省選贏取執政地位後，他則改任[[安大略省省長|省長]]麥堅迪的跨政府事務行政助理和高級顧問至2006年<ref name="Citizen140915"/><ref name="LinkedIn">{{cite web | url=https://ca.linkedin.com/in/arnold-chan-9747a010 | publisher=LinkedIn | title=Arnold Chan | accessdate=2017-09-15 }}{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。[[陳國治|陳國治]]於2007年當選萬錦－於人村選區省議員後，陳家諾出任其幕僚長至2010年<ref name="Citizen140915"/><ref name="LinkedIn"/>。[[凱斯琳·韋恩|韋恩]]於2013年當選新任安省自由黨黨魁後，陳家諾亦曾出任其過渡團隊成員<ref name="Citizen140915"/><ref name="LinkedIn"/>。

聯邦自由黨籍的[[詹嘉禮|詹嘉禮]]於2014年宣布參與多倫多市議會選舉而辭去其[[士嘉堡－愛靜閣選區|士嘉堡－愛靜閣選區]]國會議席後，陳家諾於同年5月8日贏取該選區的自由黨候選人提名<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.liberal.ca/arnold-chan-wins-lpc-nomination-scarboroughagincourt/ | publisher=[[加拿大自由黨|加拿大自由黨]] | title=Arnold Chan wins the LPC nomination for Scarborough—Agincourt | date=2014-05-09 | accessdate=2017-09-15 | archive-date=2017-09-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170915070829/https://www.liberal.ca/arnold-chan-wins-lpc-nomination-scarboroughagincourt/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>，再於同年6月30日舉行的補選中擊敗[[加拿大保守黨|聯邦保守黨]]候選人艾里斯贏取該議席，首度晉身[[加拿大國會下議院|國會下議院]]<ref name="星島140701"/><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.thestar.com/news/canada/2014/06/30/adam_vaughan_arnold_chan_lead_liberals_to_byelection_wins.html |title=Adam Vaughan, Arnold Chan lead Liberals to byelection wins |publisher=《多倫多星報》 |first=Susan |last=Delacourt |first2=Donovan |last2=Vincent |first3=Robert |last3=Benzie |date=2014-06-30 |accessdate=2017-09-15 |archive-date=2017-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170916010903/https://www.thestar.com/news/canada/2014/06/30/adam_vaughan_arnold_chan_lead_liberals_to_byelection_wins.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其後獲任命為自由黨小型企業和旅遊等範疇的評議員<ref name="parlinfo"/>。

2015年1月，陳家諾確診患上[[鼻咽癌|鼻咽癌]]<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.thestar.com/news/canada/2015/01/22/new-scarborough-mp-arnold-chan-diagnosed-with-cancer.html |title=New Scarborough MP Arnold Chan diagnosed with cancer |publisher=《多倫多星報》 |date=2015-01-22 |accessdate=2017-09-15 |archive-date=2017-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170915023320/https://www.thestar.com/news/canada/2015/01/22/new-scarborough-mp-arnold-chan-diagnosed-with-cancer.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://toronto.ctvnews.ca/scarborough-mp-diagnosed-with-cancer-1.2200598 |title=Scarborough MP diagnosed with cancer |publisher=CTV News |date=2015-01-22 |accessdate=2017-09-15 |archive-date=2017-09-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170914220221/http://toronto.ctvnews.ca/scarborough-mp-diagnosed-with-cancer-1.2200598 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，醫治半年後康復<ref name="CP160323">{{cite news | url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/toronto/scarborough-liberal-mp-arnold-chan-cancer-1.3504332 | title=Scarborough Liberal MP Arnold Chan says his cancer has returned | publisher=The Canadian Press, via CBC News | date=2016-03-23 | accessdate=2017-09-15 | archive-date=2017-09-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170917080906/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/toronto/scarborough-liberal-mp-arnold-chan-cancer-1.3504332 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。他於同年10月舉行的[[2015年加拿大聯邦大選|聯邦大選]]中連任國會議員<ref name="parlinfo"/>，同年12月獲新任[[加拿大總理|總理]][[賈斯汀·杜魯多|杜魯多]]委任為國會下議院執政黨副領袖<ref name="星島151203">{{cite news |url=http://toronto.singtao.ca/529499/2015-12-03/post-%E9%99%B3%E5%AE%B6%E8%AB%BE%E7%8D%B2%E5%A7%94%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E5%89%AF%E8%AD%B0%E9%95%B7-%E8%BA%8D%E5%8D%87%E3%80%8C%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%A7%E8%88%9E%E5%8F%B0%E3%80%8D/?variant=zh-hk |title=陳家諾獲委國會副議長 躍升「更大舞台」 |publisher=《[[星島日報|星島日報]]》加東版 |date=2015-12-03 |accessdate=2017-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170915204858/http://toronto.singtao.ca/529499/2015-12-03/post-%E9%99%B3%E5%AE%B6%E8%AB%BE%E7%8D%B2%E5%A7%94%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E5%89%AF%E8%AD%B0%E9%95%B7-%E8%BA%8D%E5%8D%87%E3%80%8C%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%A7%E8%88%9E%E5%8F%B0%E3%80%8D/?variant=zh-hk |archive-date=2017-09-15 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

陳家諾的癌病於2016年3月復發<ref name="CP160323"/>，病況於2017年中轉差<ref name="明報170915">{{cite news |url=http://www.mingpaocanada.com/Tor/htm/News/20170915/taa1_r.htm |title=抗鼻咽癌3年半不敵病魔 陳家諾50歲英年早逝 一個月前肺積水曾避一劫 遺妻子及3兒 |publisher=《[[明報|明報]]》加東版 |date=2017-09-15 |accessdate=2017-09-15 |archive-date=2017-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170915204306/http://www.mingpaocanada.com/Tor/htm/News/20170915/taa1_r.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他於同年6月最後一次在國會發言，呼籲議員摒棄「罐頭論點」並用心聆聽他人觀點，又勸籲國民珍重民主制度<ref name="星島170915">{{cite news |url=http://toronto.singtao.ca/2052383/2017-09-15/post-6%E6%9C%88%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E7%99%BC%E8%A8%80-%E5%BD%8C%E7%95%99%E4%B9%8B%E9%9A%9B%E9%97%9C%E5%BF%83%E7%A8%85%E6%94%B9-%E9%99%B3%E5%AE%B6%E8%AB%BE%E9%BC%BB%E5%92%BD%E7%99%8C/?variant=zh-hk |title=6月國會最後發言 彌留之際關心稅改 陳家諾鼻咽癌逝世 小杜難忘病榻時光 |publisher=《[[星島日報|星島日報]]》加東版 |date=2017-09-15 |accessdate=2017-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170915204940/http://toronto.singtao.ca/2052383/2017-09-15/post-6%E6%9C%88%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E7%99%BC%E8%A8%80-%E5%BD%8C%E7%95%99%E4%B9%8B%E9%9A%9B%E9%97%9C%E5%BF%83%E7%A8%85%E6%94%B9-%E9%99%B3%E5%AE%B6%E8%AB%BE%E9%BC%BB%E5%92%BD%E7%99%8C/?variant=zh-hk |archive-date=2017-09-15 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="CBC170914">{{cite news | url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/arnold-chan-death-1.4289409 | title=Liberal MP Arnold Chan dies after battle with cancer | publisher=CBC News | first=Aaron | last=Wherry | date=2017-09-14 | accessdate=2017-09-15 | archive-date=2017-09-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170915051824/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/arnold-chan-death-1.4289409 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。陳家諾於同年9月14日去世，終年50歲<ref name="明報170915"/><ref name="星島170915"/><ref name="CBC170914"/>。

==個人生活==
陳家諾與妻子[[葉嘉麗|葉嘉麗]]育有三名兒子。他去世後所懸空的國會議席於2017年12月舉行補選，由代表自由黨的葉嘉麗勝出<ref name="星島171212">{{cite news |url=http://www.singtao.ca/toronto/2252938/2017-12-12/post-%E8%B4%8F%E6%84%9B%E9%9D%9C%E9%96%A3%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%B8%AD-%E8%91%89%E5%98%89%E9%BA%97%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%88%E5%A4%AB%E6%9C%83%E9%A9%95%E5%82%B2/?variant=zh-hk |title=贏愛靜閣國會議席 葉嘉麗：先夫會驕傲 |publisher=《[[星島日報|星島日報]]》加東版 |date=2017-12-12 |accessdate=2018-02-01 }}{{Dead link|date=2019年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

